/*---------------------------------------------------------------------------*/
/* File:    c.circles                                                        */
/* Purpose: Demonstrate how to write a screensaver.                          */
/* Author:  Richard Leggett                                                  */
/* History: 14-Nov-97: RML: Created.                                         */
/*          19-Mar-98: RML: Minor changes.                                   */
